\begin_layout Section
Relative Approach
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The relative approach is highly used by practitioners, and even sometimes
 abused and misused.
 A 
\series bold
multiple
\series default
 is the paid value divided by the received value.
 The main categories of multiples are enterprise value (use FCF/NOPAT/sales/prof
it to get EV) and equity (use profit to get equity value).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
When using the multiples approach, efficient markets are assumed - prices
 reflect all relevant information.
 In addition it is assumed that the sample represents the target close enough.
\end_layout

